II. If the Judges conceive (as they may) that the taking of other mens horſes or goods is not by the Authority of Parliament, or
for the ſervice and benefit thereof, the ſouldier dies for it:
Prince, caſe, 8. reports. they may ſay to ſteale or robany man of his goods is not for the Parliaments ſervice, but againſt it.
